    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>orzo</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock </strong>and<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>basil butter </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and gently stir it all together</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
