    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> evenly on top of the orzo, they should sink down under the stock</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a generous crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for an initial 5-6 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
